public class PSSFields
extends PSDbComponentList

A simple wrapper around PSDbComponentList that simplifies use by providing the class name of the class is stored in the list.

setFields

public void setFields(Iterator fields)
Makes the supplied set of fields the only fields in this list. If any field is already present and unchanged at its equivalent ordinal position, it will not be replaced.

Parameters:
fields - the specified field set. If it is null or empty, all fields are cleared. If the iterator contains any entries, they must be PSSearchField objects.
Throws:
ClassCastException - if the objects returned by the iterator are not PSSearchFields.

removeFields
